reviews.review_text:
Jerry glad to be alive on Easter Sunday Powerful, perfectly played show from start to finish. One of the best Irvine shows and of the year imo. Jerry surely seemed revitalized and happy to be alive on this nice So. Cal. Easter Sunday. Everybody was on and this is surely a desert island pick for me. Never tire of it.

This show started at 5pm a few hours before the previous nights shows and Jerry just rips lick after lick!!!

Listen to the jam between China-Rider. Epic!

Some of Jerry's finest!
